title: The most popular baby names of 2017… so far (21 Photos)
text:
View as Slideshow 1 
According to the fine folks at nameberry.com , a baby name website, these are the baby names with the highest increase in usage in January of this year compared to 2016. This isn’t to say these names are going to replace James or Olivia anytime soon, but they do hint at the millennial generation forging a whole new cultural identity for their children. 
Or maybe they just have crap taste.
